thank you for checking out my repo. 
within crispy memory are two python games, you will need python 3 to run both games.

the first game is the is battleships you can run this from a python shell.

the second game is an alien invasion shooter game
you willl need the following files to run the game:

alien_invasion.py
alien.py
ship.py
game_functions.py
scoreboard.py
game_stats.py
settings.py
button.py 

ship.bmp
alien.bmp
